{
  "stem": "26142.16",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a terrible, terrible first impression, a sight that we saw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we all of a sudden saw through the window that a-- a group of women passed by in those Haftling pants and Haftling clothing jackets, but shaven off.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we could-- we could see that those were women, so we were sure now that this is not a-- a prisoner of war camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's a-- [SIGH]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few hours later, we were in that-- in that room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They send in about 10 or 12 [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so-called barbers and they would shave us all-- all off.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But not-- not those crazy-- regular.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, we were shaved off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And from there-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] from there, we were sent to a-- to another-- to another big hall.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have to say, it was very cold and windy on that mountain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in that other big hall, they ordered us to get undressed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So everybody used to get undressed and put together the way we did-- our shoes and our clothing, but here, they started the screams and the yellings and the beatings-- such barbaric and brutal screams.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They wanted to dehumanize the people right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could-- you could see that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't let you put-- put together your clothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if you started, getting beaten up like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we threw our clothing off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember, I had-- I had a-- a silver, very expensive watch that-- that my father had and this was-- I carried it with me and it was very sentimental for me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- I left it there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A cousin of mine in North [INAUDIBLE] gave me a-- a-- a necklace chain, a silver chain.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I forgot it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
